==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Glibbery
<hw>Glib"ber*y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Slippery; changeable.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>My love is <qex>glibbery</qex>; there is no hold on't.</q>
<rj><qau>Marston.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Moving easily; nimble; voluble.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Thy lubrical and <qex>glibbery</qex> muse.</q> <rj><qau>B.
Jonson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Glibly</ent>⟦br⟧
